      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4 text-gray-900">Why Choose Psychology Direct?</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          15+ years of excellence in psychological services
